//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/TheChemical-Brothers-Beck-new-single-collaboration-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/TheChemical-Brothers-Beck-new-single-collaboration-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/TheChemical-Brothers-Beck-new-single-collaboration-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/TheChemical-Brothers-Beck-new-single-collaboration-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/TheChemical-Brothers-Beck-new-single-collaboration-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-chemical-brothers">化学兄弟</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beck">贝克</a>合作制作了一首名为“Skipping Like A Stone”的新单曲 - 请听下面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/big-read-chemical-brothers-glastonbury-no-geography-interview-2511689"><em>NME</em>大读物 – The Chemical Brothers：“舞曲音乐一直是格拉斯顿伯里的声音”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌将出现在这对电子组合的第十张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-chemical-brothers-announce-new-album-for-that-beautiful-feeling-tracklist-preorder-3470531">“For That Beautiful Feeling”</a>中，该专辑将于 9 月 8 日通过 EMI 发行（<a href="https://thechemicalbrothers.lnk.to/FTBF" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>）。</p><p> “化学兄弟非常热衷于探索，”贝克在一份声明中解释了此次合作。</p><p> “他们在电子音乐和 DJ 文化的不同时代之间处于一个不寻常的位置。就好像他们的一只脚同时踏入了数十年，这在同龄人中是独一无二的。”</p><p>调到这里： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Chemical Brothers - Skipping Like A Stone（音频）ft. Beck" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LPhj9k9Gl2o?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>化学兄弟（又名汤姆·罗兰兹和艾德·西蒙斯）即将发布《Skipping Like A Stone》的官方音乐视频，由他们的经常合作者 Dom 和 Nic 执导。</p><p> “与化学兄弟合作是任何视频导演的梦想。几年后我们仍然一起拍电影，真的很幸运，”Dom 和 Nic 说道。</p><p> “The Chems 不断用精彩的曲目来粉碎它，这些曲目需要与音乐相匹配的视频，并希望为整个体验增添一些额外的东西。”</p><p> Beck 此前曾与 The Chemical Brothers 合作创作了他们 2015 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-the-chemical-brothers-16161-312508">《Born In The Echoes》</a>中的歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-chemical-brothers-body-morphing-video-for-wide-open-is-utterly-hypnotic-11731">《Wide Open》</a> 。</p><p>与此同时，即将推出的《For That Beautiful Feeling》是该乐队 2019 年唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/chemical-brothers-no-geography-album-review-2474740">《No Geography》</a>的后续作品。最近的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-chemical-brothers-announce-new-album-for-that-beautiful-feeling-tracklist-preorder-3470531">“Live Again”</a>也对此进行了预览。</p><p>化学兄弟将于十月前往 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-chemical-brothers-announce-2023-uk-arena-tour-3420912">英国和爱尔兰进行巡回演出</a>。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/artist/807212?utm_source=TM-google&amp;utm_medium=cpc&amp;utm_campaign=co:UK+%7C+an:The+Chemical+Brothers+%7C+obj:Sales+%7C+chl:Gn+%7C+cat:Music+%7C+bud:TM+%7C+a:5373751+%7C+pn:DF+CONCERTS+%7C+p:66+%7C+fc:IMC+%7C&amp;utm_content=paid&amp;awtrc=true&amp;utm_source=TM-google&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjw_YShBhAiEiwAMomsEE6wTrGchrYEXmI1C0AVCi92Ly3bMSsyFJaB2e2FrEFvpSsOm14QMRoC5kcQAvD_BwE&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds&amp;irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=TUeRTURCWxyNT8CXSVXWIUg%3AUkF1V2yGiX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到任何剩余的门票</a>。今年夏天，他们出现在欧洲各地的各种音乐节上，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-chemical-brothers-light-up-glastonbury-with-a-ferocious-arcadia-dj-set-3460496">2023 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-chemical-brothers-team-up-with-beck-on-new-single-skipping-like-a-stone-3486383">The Chemical Brothers 与 Beck 合作制作新单曲“Skipping Like A Stone”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
